title: CURREN CAPLES, JACK FARDELL & GREYSON FLETCHER SKATING IN SYDNEY, AUSTRALIA
description:
Curren Caples, Jack Fardell and Greyson Fletcher skating up a storm (in-between storms, too) all over Sydney Australia. The legendary Bondi Bowl-A-Rama was going on and while in town the crew made sure to have as much fun as possible...
Feb - 2013
